<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-52-1198 </DOCNO><TEXT>The authors review the heat treatment and surface hardening equipmentand technology used by the Mogilev metal enterprises in the productionof heavy equipment. Specific information is given on spray and diffusioncoating technology and the effects of a variety of metals, includingboron and chromium, on the hardness and wear resistance of the coatedalloys. Suggestions are also tendered for automation and optimizationof the processes.</TEXT></DOC>